[SHORT DESC]
Raises Chansey's critical hit ratio two stages.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Raises Chansey's critical hit ratio by two stages.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>This item should only be used for trolling or on April Fools' Day. Not only does Chansey have an abysmal Attack and Special Attack, it also should not be used in the first place without Eviolite.</p>

<h2>Location</h2>
<p>Route 13 (talk to Treasure Hunter - you receive one random treasure every day).</p>